metadata.description: Welcome to the Shiba Puppy Metaverse..! We have 3344 exciting and beautifully drawn NFTs that are the keys to unlocking Utility and long term value. So in addition to proudly showing off your Shiba Puppies, you can also benefit from passive income with our Staking app and community wallet. Our ultimate goal is to have everyone meet up in the Metaverse with your Shiba Puppy Metaverse NFT as the key to your access and your future adventures
